<view class="container">

<!-- 顶部Logo和标题 -->
<view class="header">
  <image src="/assets/images/logo.jpg" class="logo" mode="aspectFit"></image>
  <text class="title">畲韵传声</text>
</view>

<!-- 图片展示区 -->
<swiper class="image-swiper" autoplay interval="3000" circular>
  <swiper-item>
    <image src="/assets/images/banner1.jpg" class="banner-img"></image>
  </swiper-item>
  <swiper-item>
    <image src="/assets/images/banner2.jpg" class="banner-img"></image>
  </swiper-item>
  <swiper-item>
    <image src="/assets/images/banner3.jpg" class="banner-img"></image>
  </swiper-item>
</swiper>

<!-- 简介信息 -->
<view class="intro">
  <text>
    畲族是中国南方一个历史悠久的民族，以歌传情、以舞载史。
    本小程序旨在传播畲族文化，展示民歌、风俗与精神。
  </text>
</view>

<!-- 导航区域 -->
<view class="nav-area">
  <!-- 民歌视频专区 -->
  <view class="nav-card" bindtap="goToVideos">
    <image src="/assets/icons/music.png" class="nav-icon"></image>
    <view class="nav-text">
      <text class="nav-title">民歌视频专区</text>
      <text class="nav-subtitle">观看与学习畲族民歌</text>
    </view>
    <image src="/assets/icons/arrow-right.png" class="arrow-icon"></image>
  </view>

  <!-- 畲族文化介绍 -->
  <view class="nav-card" bindtap="goToCulture">
    <image src="/assets/icons/book.png" class="nav-icon"></image>
    <view class="nav-text">
      <text class="nav-title">畲族文化介绍</text>
      <text class="nav-subtitle">了解畲族的历史与风俗</text>
    </view>
    <image src="/assets/icons/arrow-right.png" class="arrow-icon"></image>
  </view>
</view>

</view>
